{% doc %}
  @prompt
    I want you to design a section similar to the featured product section of Shopify, but obviously with a modern, sleek, and e-commerce-oriented beautiful design. The section will have a heading first, and then it will have a grid of 4 (for the laptop version), and every grid hosts a product card. The card has an image of the product, then the title of the product, then a small subtle tag (for example, like "Unstitched | New Arrival"), and then the price of the product (also the discounted price, other, or cut price, or compare price option, whatever you call it—designed in a very minimalist and subtle manner). Then the product star rating or rating in a unique way is designed, and a beautiful, homogenous button is created. The overall design of the section must be a sleek, modern, mimialist and elegant e-commerce UI. Also, provide the control option for everything for every text, heading, image, heading, tag, button, ratings, price text, layout of section (like all side margins, all side paddings, size, colour, font-weight, line height, grid gap, image properties like object-fit, object position, image box shadow( and other important CSS styling properties for full accessibility for customization), and the section must be mobile- and tablet-responsive and provide full control all Css styling properies available(as for desktop version) for the mobile- and tablet versions also so I can tweak things a bit accordingly. Other than the button option, make the whole card a clickable item. Apply some beautiful and modern animation on the cards. Provide the display on/off option for the sale tag (that will be on the card image), the button, the rating stars, and the small tag beneath the description. and make the cards or section compatible with the Shopify system. Just like in the conventional featured product section, the whole already-made collection is displayed in cards; rather than adding the data manually in the cards, the data from the pre-made collection automatically fills in. Regarding the button on the card - it can be a modern minimalist button designed with a pretty thin and sleek arrow icon inside a small circle, placed in the bottom right corner of the card, or placed somewhere (like the top right corner) on the card's image (I have also provided a reference image to see how this button will be designed and placed). Lastly, after the grid part, there will be a button to view all., Rest, everything is fine; just add one more thing: add the input text field for the tag text for every card separately. and shift the star rating upward and the price at the very end. , The product tag should remain beneath the product title. (stack: product title then product tag, then ratings, then price
{% enddoc %}
{% assign ai_gen_id = block.id | replace: '_', '' | downcase %}

{% style %}
/* Code has been pushed Successfully */
  .ai-featured-collection-{{ ai_gen_id }} {
    display: block;
    width: 100%;
    padding: {{ block.settings.section_padding_top_desktop }}px {{ block.settings.section_padding_horizontal_desktop }}px {{ block.settings.section_padding_bottom_desktop }}px;
    background-color: {{ block.settings.section_background_color }};
  }

  .ai-featured-collection__container-{{ ai_gen_id }} {
    max-width: {{ block.settings.container_max_width }}px;
    margin: 0 auto;
  }

  .ai-featured-collection__header-{{ ai_gen_id }} {
    text-align: {{ block.settings.heading_alignment }};
    margin-bottom: {{ block.settings.heading_margin_bottom_desktop }}px;
  }

  .ai-featured-collection__heading-{{ ai_gen_id }} {
    font-size: {{ block.settings.heading_font_size_desktop }}px;
    font-weight: {{ block.settings.heading_font_weight }};
    line-height: {{ block.settings.heading_line_height }};
    color: {{ block.settings.heading_color }};
    margin: 0;
  }

  .ai-featured-collection__grid-{{ ai_gen_id }} {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: repeat({{ block.settings.columns_desktop }}, 1fr);
    gap: {{ block.settings.grid_gap_desktop }}px;
    margin-bottom: {{ block.settings.grid_margin_bottom_desktop }}px;
  }

  .ai-featured-collection__card-{{ ai_gen_id }} {
    position: relative;
    background-color: {{ block.settings.card_background_color }};
    border-radius: {{ block.settings.card_border_radius }}px;
    overflow: hidden;
    transition: transform 0.3s ease, box-shadow 0.3s ease;
    box-shadow: {{ block.settings.card_shadow_horizontal }}px {{ block.settings.card_shadow_vertical }}px {{ block.settings.card_shadow_blur }}px {{ block.settings.card_shadow_color }};
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    text-decoration: none;
    color: inherit;
  }

  .ai-featured-collection__card-{{ ai_gen_id }}:hover {
    transform: translateY({{ block.settings.card_hover_translate_y }}px);
    box-shadow: {{ block.settings.card_hover_shadow_horizontal }}px {{ block.settings.card_hover_shadow_vertical }}px {{ block.settings.card_hover_shadow_blur }}px {{ block.settings.card_hover_shadow_color }};
  }

  .ai-featured-collection__image-wrapper-{{ ai_gen_id }} {
    position: relative;
    width: 100%;
    padding-top: {{ block.settings.image_aspect_ratio }}%;
    overflow: hidden;
    background-color: {{ block.settings.image_background_color }};
  }

  .ai-featured-collection__image-{{ ai_gen_id }} {
    position: absolute;
    top: 0;
    left: 0;
    width: 100%;
    height: 100%;
    object-fit: {{ block.settings.image_object_fit }};
    object-position: {{ block.settings.image_object_position }};
    transition: transform 0.3s ease;
  }

  .ai-featured-collection__card-{{ ai_gen_id }}:hover .ai-featured-collection__image-{{ ai_gen_id }} {
    transform: scale({{ block.settings.image_hover_scale }});
  }

  .ai-featured-collection__sale-badge-{{ ai_gen_id }} {
    position: absolute;
    top: {{ block.settings.sale_badge_top }}px;
    left: {{ block.settings.sale_badge_left }}px;
    background-color: {{ block.settings.sale_badge_background }};
    color: {{ block.settings.sale_badge_text_color }};
    padding: {{ block.settings.sale_badge_padding_vertical }}px {{ block.settings.sale_badge_padding_horizontal }}px;
    border-radius: {{ block.settings.sale_badge_border_radius }}px;
    font-size: {{ block.settings.sale_badge_font_size }}px;
    font-weight: {{ block.settings.sale_badge_font_weight }};
    z-index: 2;
  }

  .ai-featured-collection__arrow-button-{{ ai_gen_id }} {
    position: absolute;
    {% if block.settings.arrow_button_position == 'bottom-right' %}
      bottom: {{ block.settings.arrow_button_offset }}px;
      right: {{ block.settings.arrow_button_offset }}px;
    {% elsif block.settings.arrow_button_position == 'top-right' %}
      top: {{ block.settings.arrow_button_offset }}px;
      right: {{ block.settings.arrow_button_offset }}px;
    {% elsif block.settings.arrow_button_position == 'top-left' %}
      top: {{ block.settings.arrow_button_offset }}px;
      left: {{ block.settings.arrow_button_offset }}px;
    {% else %}
      bottom: {{ block.settings.arrow_button_offset }}px;
      left: {{ block.settings.arrow_button_offset }}px;
    {% endif %}
    width: {{ block.settings.arrow_button_size }}px;
    height: {{ block.settings.arrow_button_size }}px;
    border-radius: 50%;
    background-color: {{ block.settings.arrow_button_background }};
    border: {{ block.settings.arrow_button_border_width }}px solid {{ block.settings.arrow_button_border_color }};
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    justify-content: center;
    z-index: 3;
    transition: background-color 0.3s ease, transform 0.3s ease;
    cursor: pointer;
  }

  .ai-featured-collection__card-{{ ai_gen_id }}:hover .ai-featured-collection__arrow-button-{{ ai_gen_id }} {
    background-color: {{ block.settings.arrow_button_hover_background }};
    transform: scale(1.1);
  }

  .ai-featured-collection__arrow-icon-{{ ai_gen_id }} {
    width: {{ block.settings.arrow_icon_size }}px;
    height: {{ block.settings.arrow_icon_size }}px;
    stroke: {{ block.settings.arrow_icon_color }};
    stroke-width: {{ block.settings.arrow_icon_stroke_width }};
  }

  .ai-featured-collection__content-{{ ai_gen_id }} {
    padding: {{ block.settings.card_content_padding_desktop }}px;
    flex-grow: 1;
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
  }

  .ai-featured-collection__title-{{ ai_gen_id }} {
    font-size: {{ block.settings.title_font_size_desktop }}px;
    font-weight: {{ block.settings.title_font_weight }};
    line-height: {{ block.settings.title_line_height }};
    color: {{ block.settings.title_color }};
    margin: 0 0 {{ block.settings.title_margin_bottom }}px;
  }

  .ai-featured-collection__tag-{{ ai_gen_id }} {
    font-size: {{ block.settings.tag_font_size }}px;
    font-weight: {{ block.settings.tag_font_weight }};
    color: {{ block.settings.tag_color }};
    margin-bottom: {{ block.settings.tag_margin_bottom }}px;
    opacity: 0.7;
  }

  .ai-featured-collection__rating-{{ ai_gen_id }} {
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    gap: {{ block.settings.rating_gap }}px;
    margin-bottom: {{ block.settings.rating_margin_bottom }}px;
  }

  .ai-featured-collection__stars-{{ ai_gen_id }} {
    display: flex;
    gap: {{ block.settings.star_gap }}px;
  }

  .ai-featured-collection__star-{{ ai_gen_id }} {
    width: {{ block.settings.star_size }}px;
    height: {{ block.settings.star_size }}px;
    fill: {{ block.settings.star_color }};
  }

  .ai-featured-collection__star-empty-{{ ai_gen_id }} {
    fill: {{ block.settings.star_empty_color }};
  }

  .ai-featured-collection__rating-count-{{ ai_gen_id }} {
    font-size: {{ block.settings.rating_count_font_size }}px;
    color: {{ block.settings.rating_count_color }};
    opacity: 0.7;
  }

  .ai-featured-collection__price-wrapper-{{ ai_gen_id }} {
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    gap: {{ block.settings.price_gap }}px;
    margin-top: auto;
  }

  .ai-featured-collection__price-{{ ai_gen_id }} {
    font-size: {{ block.settings.price_font_size_desktop }}px;
    font-weight: {{ block.settings.price_font_weight }};
    color: {{ block.settings.price_color }};
  }

  .ai-featured-collection__compare-price-{{ ai_gen_id }} {
    font-size: {{ block.settings.compare_price_font_size }}px;
    font-weight: {{ block.settings.compare_price_font_weight }};
    color: {{ block.settings.compare_price_color }};
    text-decoration: line-through;
    opacity: 0.6;
  }

  .ai-featured-collection__view-all-wrapper-{{ ai_gen_id }} {
    text-align: {{ block.settings.view_all_alignment }};
  }

  .ai-featured-collection__view-all-{{ ai_gen_id }} {
    display: inline-flex;
    align-items: center;
    justify-content: center;
    padding: {{ block.settings.view_all_padding_vertical }}px {{ block.settings.view_all_padding_horizontal }}px;
    background-color: {{ block.settings.view_all_background }};
    color: {{ block.settings.view_all_text_color }};
    border: {{ block.settings.view_all_border_width }}px solid {{ block.settings.view_all_border_color }};
    border-radius: {{ block.settings.view_all_border_radius }}px;
    font-size: {{ block.settings.view_all_font_size }}px;
    font-weight: {{ block.settings.view_all_font_weight }};
    text-decoration: none;
    transition: background-color 0.3s ease, color 0.3s ease, transform 0.3s ease;
  }

  .ai-featured-collection__view-all-{{ ai_gen_id }}:hover {
    background-color: {{ block.settings.view_all_hover_background }};
    color: {{ block.settings.view_all_hover_text_color }};
    transform: translateY(-2px);
  }

  @media screen and (max-width: 989px) {
    .ai-featured-collection-{{ ai_gen_id }} {
      padding: {{ block.settings.section_padding_top_tablet }}px {{ block.settings.section_padding_horizontal_tablet }}px {{ block.settings.section_padding_bottom_tablet }}px;
    }

    .ai-featured-collection__heading-{{ ai_gen_id }} {
      font-size: {{ block.settings.heading_font_size_tablet }}px;
      margin-bottom: {{ block.settings.heading_margin_bottom_tablet }}px;
    }

    .ai-featured-collection__grid-{{ ai_gen_id }} {
      grid-template-columns: repeat({{ block.settings.columns_tablet }}, 1fr);
      gap: {{ block.settings.grid_gap_tablet }}px;
      margin-bottom: {{ block.settings.grid_margin_bottom_tablet }}px;
    }

    .ai-featured-collection__content-{{ ai_gen_id }} {
      padding: {{ block.settings.card_content_padding_tablet }}px;
    }

    .ai-featured-collection__title-{{ ai_gen_id }} {
      font-size: {{ block.settings.title_font_size_tablet }}px;
    }

    .ai-featured-collection__price-{{ ai_gen_id }} {
      font-size: {{ block.settings.price_font_size_tablet }}px;
    }
  }

  @media screen and (max-width: 749px) {
    .ai-featured-collection-{{ ai_gen_id }} {
      padding: {{ block.settings.section_padding_top_mobile }}px {{ block.settings.section_padding_horizontal_mobile }}px {{ block.settings.section_padding_bottom_mobile }}px;
    }

    .ai-featured-collection__heading-{{ ai_gen_id }} {
      font-size: {{ block.settings.heading_font_size_mobile }}px;
      margin-bottom: {{ block.settings.heading_margin_bottom_mobile }}px;
    }

    .ai-featured-collection__grid-{{ ai_gen_id }} {
      grid-template-columns: repeat({{ block.settings.columns_mobile }}, 1fr);
      gap: {{ block.settings.grid_gap_mobile }}px;
      margin-bottom: {{ block.settings.grid_margin_bottom_mobile }}px;
    }

    .ai-featured-collection__content-{{ ai_gen_id }} {
      padding: {{ block.settings.card_content_padding_mobile }}px;
    }

    .ai-featured-collection__title-{{ ai_gen_id }} {
      font-size: {{ block.settings.title_font_size_mobile }}px;
    }

    .ai-featured-collection__price-{{ ai_gen_id }} {
      font-size: {{ block.settings.price_font_size_mobile }}px;
    }
  }
{% endstyle %}

<featured-collection-{{ ai_gen_id }} class="ai-featured-collection-{{ ai_gen_id }}" {{ block.shopify_attributes }}>
  <div class="ai-featured-collection__container-{{ ai_gen_id }}">
    {% if block.settings.heading != blank %}
      <div class="ai-featured-collection__header-{{ ai_gen_id }}">
        <h2 class="ai-featured-collection__heading-{{ ai_gen_id }}">{{ block.settings.heading }}</h2>
      </div>
    {% endif %}

    {% if block.settings.collection != blank %}
      <div class="ai-featured-collection__grid-{{ ai_gen_id }}">
        {% for product in block.settings.collection.products limit: block.settings.products_to_show %}
          {% assign product_index = forloop.index %}
          {% assign custom_tag_key = 'product_' | append: product_index | append: '_custom_tag' %}
          {% assign custom_tag = block.settings[custom_tag_key] %}

          <a href="{{ product.url }}" class="ai-featured-collection__card-{{ ai_gen_id }}">
            <div class="ai-featured-collection__image-wrapper-{{ ai_gen_id }}">
              {% if product.featured_image %}
                <img
                  src="{{ product.featured_image | image_url: width: 800 }}"
                  alt="{{ product.featured_image.alt | escape }}"
                  class="ai-featured-collection__image-{{ ai_gen_id }}"
                  loading="lazy"
                  width="800"
                  height="{{ 800 | divided_by: product.featured_image.aspect_ratio | round }}"
                >
              {% else %}
                <div class="ai-featured-collection__image-placeholder-{{ ai_gen_id }}">
                  {{ 'product-1' | placeholder_svg_tag }}
                </div>
              {% endif %}

              {% assign current_variant = product.selected_or_first_available_variant %}
              {% assign has_discount = false %}
              {% assign discount_percent = 0 %}

              {% if current_variant.compare_at_price > current_variant.price %}
                {% assign has_discount = true %}
                {% assign discount_amount = current_variant.compare_at_price | minus: current_variant.price %}
                {% assign discount_raw = discount_amount | times: 100 | divided_by: current_variant.compare_at_price %}
                {% assign discount_percent = discount_raw | round %}
              {% endif %}

              {% if block.settings.show_sale_badge and has_discount %}
                <div class="ai-featured-collection__sale-badge-{{ ai_gen_id }}">{{ discount_percent }}% OFF</div>
              {% endif %}

              {% if block.settings.show_arrow_button %}
                <div class="ai-featured-collection__arrow-button-{{ ai_gen_id }}">
                  <svg
                    class="ai-featured-collection__arrow-icon-{{ ai_gen_id }}"
                    viewBox="0 0 24 24"
                    fill="none"
                    xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg"
                  >
                    <path d="M5 12H19M19 12L12 5M19 12L12 19" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"/>
                  </svg>
                </div>
              {% endif %}
            </div>

            <div class="ai-featured-collection__content-{{ ai_gen_id }}">
              <h3 class="ai-featured-collection__title-{{ ai_gen_id }}">{{ product.title }}</h3>

              {% if block.settings.show_product_tag %}
                <div class="ai-featured-collection__tag-{{ ai_gen_id }}">
                  {{ product.selected_or_first_available_variant.title | escape }}
                </div>
              {% endif %}

              {% if block.settings.show_rating %}
                <div class="ai-featured-collection__rating-{{ ai_gen_id }}">
                  <div class="ai-featured-collection__stars-{{ ai_gen_id }}">
                    {% assign rating = block.settings.default_rating %}
                    {% for i in (1..5) %}
                      {% if i <= rating %}
                        <svg
                          class="ai-featured-collection__star-{{ ai_gen_id }}"
                          viewBox="0 0 24 24"
                          xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg"
                        >
                          <path d="M12 2L15.09 8.26L22 9.27L17 14.14L18.18 21.02L12 17.77L5.82 21.02L7 14.14L2 9.27L8.91 8.26L12 2Z"/>
                        </svg>
                      {% else %}
                        <svg
                          class="ai-featured-collection__star-{{ ai_gen_id }} ai-featured-collection__star-empty-{{ ai_gen_id }}"
                          viewBox="0 0 24 24"
                          xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg"
                        >
                          <path d="M12 2L15.09 8.26L22 9.27L17 14.14L18.18 21.02L12 17.77L5.82 21.02L7 14.14L2 9.27L8.91 8.26L12 2Z"/>
                        </svg>
                      {% endif %}
                    {% endfor %}
                  </div>
                  {% if block.settings.show_rating_count %}
                    <span class="ai-featured-collection__rating-count-{{ ai_gen_id }}"
                      >({{ block.settings.rating_count_text }})</span
                    >
                  {% endif %}
                </div>
              {% endif %}

              <div class="ai-featured-collection__price-wrapper-{{ ai_gen_id }}">
                <span class="ai-featured-collection__price-{{ ai_gen_id }}">
                  {{ product.price | money }}
                </span>
                {% if product.compare_at_price > product.price %}
                  <span class="ai-featured-collection__compare-price-{{ ai_gen_id }}">
                    {{ product.compare_at_price | money }}
                  </span>
                {% endif %}
              </div>
            </div>
          </a>
        {% endfor %}
      </div>

      {% if block.settings.show_view_all_button %}
        <div class="ai-featured-collection__view-all-wrapper-{{ ai_gen_id }}">
          <a href="{{ block.settings.collection.url }}" class="ai-featured-collection__view-all-{{ ai_gen_id }}">
            {{ block.settings.view_all_button_text }}
          </a>
        </div>
      {% endif %}
    {% else %}
      <div
        class="ai-featured-collection__empty-state-{{ ai_gen_id }}"
        style="text-align: center; padding: 60px 20px; color: #999;"
      >
        <p style="font-size: 16px; margin: 0;">Select a collection to display products</p>
      </div>
    {% endif %}
  </div>
</featured-collection-{{ ai_gen_id }}>

<script>
  (function() {
    class FeaturedCollection{{ ai_gen_id }} extends HTMLElement {
      constructor() {
        super();
      }

      connectedCallback() {
        this.cards = this.querySelectorAll('.ai-featured-collection__card-{{ ai_gen_id }}');
        this.setupCardInteractions();
      }

      setupCardInteractions() {
        this.cards.forEach((card) => {
          const arrowButton = card.querySelector('.ai-featured-collection__arrow-button-{{ ai_gen_id }}');

          if (arrowButton) {
            arrowButton.addEventListener('click', (e) => {
              e.preventDefault();
              e.stopPropagation();
              window.location.href = card.href;
            });
          }
        });
      }
    }

    customElements.define('featured-collection-{{ ai_gen_id }}', FeaturedCollection{{ ai_gen_id }});
  })();
</script>

{% schema %}
{
  "name": "Featured collection",
  "settings": [
    {
      "type": "header",
      "content": "Collection"
    },
    {
      "type": "collection",
      "id": "collection",
      "label": "Collection"
    },
    {
      "type": "range",
      "id": "products_to_show",
      "min": 2,
      "max": 12,
      "step": 1,
      "label": "Products to show",
      "default": 4
    },
    {
      "type": "header",
      "content": "Section heading"
    },
    {
      "type": "text",
      "id": "heading",
      "label": "Heading",
      "default": "Featured Products"
    },
    {
      "type": "select",
      "id": "heading_alignment",
      "label": "Heading alignment",
      "options": [
        { "value": "left", "label": "Left" },
        { "value": "center", "label": "Center" },
        { "value": "right", "label": "Right" }
      ],
      "default": "center"
    },
    {
      "type": "color",
      "id": "heading_color",
      "label": "Heading color",
      "default": "#2e2a39"
    },
    {
      "type": "range",
      "id": "heading_font_size_desktop",
      "min": 20,
      "max": 80,
      "step": 2,
      "unit": "px",
      "label": "Heading size (desktop)",
      "default": 40
    },
    {
      "type": "range",
      "id": "heading_font_size_tablet",
